Come sit with us.

836
00:45:59,720 --> 00:46:00,880
Qin's friend is also mine.

837
00:46:00,920 --> 00:46:01,480
Facts.

838
00:46:02,240 --> 00:46:03,320
Can I have this stool?

839
00:46:05,560 --> 00:46:06,840
I'm not holding back, then.

840
00:46:07,560 --> 00:46:08,360
Waiter,

841
00:46:08,400 --> 00:46:12,480
one plate, one spoon,
one pair of chopsticks, please.

842
00:46:13,960 --> 00:46:15,160
Oh, where are you going?

843
00:46:15,800 --> 00:46:16,600
To grab some desserts.

844
00:46:16,640 --> 00:46:17,560
I'll come with you.

845
00:46:28,080 --> 00:46:28,960
Sup, bro.

846
00:46:30,790 --> 00:46:31,790
Sup, bro.

847
00:46:36,560 --> 00:46:38,000
Cho, were you
Qin's friend in high school?

848
00:46:38,520 --> 00:46:40,520
Yeah, we were
in a marching band together.

849
00:46:40,960 --> 00:46:42,600
So how was Qin back then?

850
00:46:43,160 --> 00:46:44,160
Whoa...

851
00:46:45,400 --> 00:46:46,400
studious,

852
00:46:46,440 --> 00:46:47,500
good-looking,

853
00:46:47,540 --> 00:46:48,400
athletic,

854
00:46:48,620 --> 00:46:50,480
and a teachers' fav.

855
00:46:51,200 --> 00:46:52,200
Aw...

856
00:46:52,380 --> 00:46:54,040
How flawless of you, Qin.

857
00:46:54,160 --> 00:46:54,920
Yeah.

858
00:46:55,120 --> 00:46:57,120
So were you a hot guy?

859
00:46:57,800 --> 00:46:59,480
That's enough.
I'm still sitting right here.

860
00:47:00,240 --> 00:47:01,720
He was so freaking hot,
let me tell you that.

861
00:47:01,920 --> 00:47:03,400
But he didn't seem to care about anyone,

862
00:47:03,960 --> 00:47:05,920
except my friend,

863
00:47:06,680 --> 00:47:07,560
Tiw.

864
00:47:12,640 --> 00:47:14,200
Just let me talk about him please.

865
00:47:14,240 --> 00:47:15,480
It was a long time ago.

866
00:47:16,160 --> 00:47:17,400
And you two already broke up.

867
00:47:18,640 --> 00:47:20,280
We didn't break up or anything.

868
00:47:21,120 --> 00:47:22,280
Fine, you didn't.

869
00:47:22,960 --> 00:47:24,080
But here's something spicy.

870
00:47:24,200 --> 00:47:25,840
No way!

871
00:47:26,680 --> 00:47:30,110
Tiw, my friend, gave Qin a teddy bear

872
00:47:30,480 --> 00:47:31,680
in front of everyone at school.

873
00:47:32,360 --> 00:47:35,040
He wanted everyone
to know Qin was his.

874
00:47:40,640 --> 00:47:41,640
Right.

875
00:47:42,080 --> 00:47:43,590
It was all in the past, right?

876
00:47:43,960 --> 00:47:45,280
Let's talk about something else.

877
00:47:45,520 --> 00:47:46,520
That's right!

878
00:47:48,160 --> 00:47:49,200
But...

879
00:47:52,160 --> 00:47:53,560
If you want to get back with him,

880
00:47:54,280 --> 00:47:55,320
feel free to tell me.

881
00:47:56,160 --> 00:47:57,600
Shut up and finish your bowl.

882
00:47:59,960 --> 00:48:01,680
You're still as harsh as ever, I guess.

883
00:48:03,040 --> 00:48:04,400
Duang needs your help.

884
00:48:07,000 --> 00:48:08,680
Qin, is the grass jelly good?

885
00:48:10,480 --> 00:48:11,240
It's decent.

886
00:48:12,400 --> 00:48:13,400
Do you want another bowl?

887
00:48:14,760 --> 00:48:16,160
- Let me...
- What do you think of Duang?

888
00:48:18,720 --> 00:48:19,920
Oh, shit.

889
00:48:22,280 --> 00:48:23,640
Duang and Qin are...

890
00:48:23,920 --> 00:48:25,600
It's just like what you're thinking.

891
00:48:26,720 --> 00:48:27,720
Ding, ding.

892
00:48:30,240 --> 00:48:31,160
Damn.

893
00:48:31,640 --> 00:48:32,840
I'm so sorry.

894
00:48:33,000 --> 00:48:34,880
Oh, it's okay!

895
00:48:34,920 --> 00:48:35,840
It's fine.

896
00:48:36,240 --> 00:48:37,480
Right, right, right.

897
00:48:37,840 --> 00:48:40,840
So, Qin, what do you think of Duang?

898
00:48:52,360 --> 00:48:54,240
I'll get you another bowl.

899
00:49:00,580 --> 00:49:02,320
Duang is too naive, Qin.

900
00:49:02,480 --> 00:49:03,960
If you don't tell him,
he'll never know.

901
00:49:04,880 --> 00:49:06,560
He's extremely clueless.

902
00:49:06,600 --> 00:49:07,600
Yeah.

903
00:49:07,880 --> 00:49:08,940
Isn't that right?

904
00:49:10,800 --> 00:49:11,720
Clueless.

905
00:49:13,280 --> 00:49:14,680
Hey, I think I should leave.

906
00:49:15,000 --> 00:49:16,720
I'll pay you later.
Just tell me how much.

907
00:49:17,760 --> 00:49:19,160
Wait.

908
00:49:22,720 --> 00:49:24,120
Pay up right now.

909
00:49:24,160 --> 00:49:26,080
319 baht.

910
00:49:27,160 --> 00:49:28,760
319 baht...

911
00:49:31,520 --> 00:49:32,280
There!

912
00:49:32,520 --> 00:49:33,440
Hey, wait!

913
00:49:35,160 --> 00:49:36,240
Why are you just standing there?

914
00:49:36,280 --> 00:49:37,080
Follow him.

915
00:49:37,600 --> 00:49:38,880
There goes your 319 baht.

916
00:49:39,400 --> 00:49:40,480
It's fine.
We'll split the bill, alright?

917
00:50:00,240 --> 00:50:00,920
Guys.

918
00:50:01,360 --> 00:50:02,240
I've got to go now.

919
00:50:02,480 --> 00:50:03,480
I need to get back to my crush.

920
00:50:04,040 --> 00:50:05,960
- Bye-bye.
- Oh, bye-bye.

921
00:50:06,000 --> 00:50:08,400
Qin, I'm completely hammered.

922
00:50:10,760 --> 00:50:11,960
We didn't order any alcohol!

923
00:50:12,000 --> 00:50:13,000
You're so pretentious.

924
00:50:13,420 --> 00:50:14,960
What a cheeky little guy.

925
00:50:15,440 --> 00:50:16,360
Aww...

926
00:50:16,520 --> 00:50:17,400
You caught me.

927
00:50:18,980 --> 00:50:20,480
Would it kill you
to stop teasing me for a day?

928
00:50:21,430 --> 00:50:22,080
Oh?!

929
00:50:22,120 --> 00:50:22,880
Qin smiled!

930
00:50:26,960 --> 00:50:29,120
You lied to me again.
You're such a bad friend.

931
00:50:30,080 --> 00:50:31,080
Stop fighting.

932
00:50:31,120 --> 00:50:32,000
I have to go as well.

933
00:50:35,240 --> 00:50:36,240
I'll take you home.

934
00:50:38,300 --> 00:50:39,200
I've already called a ride.

935
00:50:41,880 --> 00:50:43,120
Qin already called his ride,

936
00:50:43,160 --> 00:50:44,440
but I haven't.

937
00:50:44,480 --> 00:50:45,320
Take me home instead, okay?

938
00:50:46,760 --> 00:50:47,760
Are you Qin?

939
00:50:48,360 --> 00:50:49,280
I refuse.

940
00:50:49,320 --> 00:50:50,240
What?!

941
00:50:50,640 --> 00:50:51,800
Well then...

942
00:50:52,720 --> 00:50:55,600
Qin, let me use your name for a bit.

943
00:50:59,480 --> 00:51:01,080
Duang, call me Qin.

944
00:51:02,320 --> 00:51:03,160
I'll be going now.

945
00:51:05,080 --> 00:51:06,080
Bye-bye.

946
00:51:06,840 --> 00:51:08,440
Bye-bye!

947
00:51:09,520 --> 00:51:10,120
Oh?

948
00:51:10,380 --> 00:51:11,180
I should go home as well.

949
00:51:14,560 --> 00:51:16,080
My name is Qin.

950
00:51:16,200 --> 00:51:16,920
Now, take me home.

951
00:51:17,120 --> 00:51:18,120
Hell no.

952
00:51:18,300 --> 00:51:20,440
Huh? What do you mean?

953
00:51:20,480 --> 00:51:21,680
I'm Qin now.

954
00:51:22,280 --> 00:51:23,120
You're so pretentious.

955
00:51:23,160 --> 00:51:24,000
Head home on your own.

956
00:51:24,040 --> 00:51:24,920
By the way, we're friends.

957
00:51:24,960 --> 00:51:25,960
Temporarily not.

958
00:51:26,080 --> 00:51:27,240
Tit for tat.

959
00:51:27,440 --> 00:51:28,600
Fair's fair.

960
00:51:32,200 --> 00:51:33,040
Duang!

961
00:51:46,280 --> 00:51:47,440
Why are you following me?

962
00:51:47,640 --> 00:51:48,320
Huh?

963
00:51:48,800 --> 00:51:50,080
It's none of your business.

964
00:51:50,760 --> 00:51:51,640
Fine, damn it.

965
00:51:51,680 --> 00:51:52,800
If you're so tough,
get home on your own.

966
00:51:54,040 --> 00:51:55,920
Don't try to act tough with me, Duang.

967
00:51:57,760 --> 00:51:59,200
A stranger

968
00:51:59,240 --> 00:52:00,840
addressing someone inappropriately...

969
00:52:00,880 --> 00:52:02,240
How ill-mannered.

970
00:52:08,760 --> 00:52:11,360
If I were not this well-behaved...

971
00:52:12,440 --> 00:52:13,240
What?

972
00:52:13,480 --> 00:52:14,640
What would you have done?

973
00:52:15,200 --> 00:52:16,320
Look at what you've done to me.

974
00:52:16,360 --> 00:52:19,000
I'd soak my shoes in water

975
00:52:19,040 --> 00:52:21,200
and kick the shit out of you.

976
00:52:21,240 --> 00:52:22,440
Get ready for it.

977
00:52:22,480 --> 00:52:23,360
Get the hell away from me!

978
00:52:28,240 --> 00:52:30,400
What did I do to upset you, huh?

979
00:52:31,960 --> 00:52:34,520
You leaned on Qin's shoulder.

980
00:52:34,560 --> 00:52:36,360
And you talked to him too much!

981
00:52:37,520 --> 00:52:39,720
You're going to hit on him
even though you know he's my crush?

982
00:52:42,280 --> 00:52:43,040
Gosh.

983
00:52:43,520 --> 00:52:44,520
This is hilarious.

984
00:52:45,000 --> 00:52:46,760
Why are you this upset?

985
00:52:48,200 --> 00:52:50,040
Stop laughing, damn it.

986
00:52:53,000 --> 00:52:55,320
Instead of being mad at me,

987
00:52:55,360 --> 00:52:58,200
you should think about Qin's teddy.

988
00:52:58,480 --> 00:52:59,160
Right?

989
00:53:01,920 --> 00:53:03,040
Yeah, you're right.

990
00:53:04,140 --> 00:53:05,800
I don't know what to do next.

991
00:53:06,840 --> 00:53:08,440
He still keeps that teddy.

992
00:53:10,240 --> 00:53:11,240
Oh, you.

993
00:53:11,800 --> 00:53:13,480
You're taking it out on me?

994
00:53:18,080 --> 00:53:19,400
Qin...

995
00:53:21,760 --> 00:53:23,400
What the hell are you saying?

996
00:53:23,800 --> 00:53:25,480
Stop crying like a wet puppy.

997
00:53:25,920 --> 00:53:26,520
Hush!

998
00:53:26,800 --> 00:53:27,560
Hush, hush...

999
00:53:27,600 --> 00:53:28,560
Hush! Hush!

1000
00:53:39,680 --> 00:53:42,440
At first, I didn't think
his walls were that high.

1001
00:53:43,240 --> 00:53:44,640
I thought I could get over them,

1002
00:53:45,080 --> 00:53:46,280
but I guess I was delusional.

1003
00:53:48,600 --> 00:53:52,000
But you're the first
to stand up to his walls.

1004
00:53:59,880 --> 00:54:02,360
Does keeping the teddy around
really mean nothing at all?

1005
00:54:04,040 --> 00:54:05,280
So...

1006
00:54:05,320 --> 00:54:06,800
You're giving up?

1007
00:54:12,920 --> 00:54:14,320
I'm worried about Qin.

1008
00:54:15,640 --> 00:54:17,360
I'm worried he'd choose that person.

1009
00:54:18,440 --> 00:54:21,080
I'm worried he'd come up to me
and reject me.

1010
00:54:22,920 --> 00:54:24,720
I don't know
what I'm supposed to do now.

1011
00:54:30,320 --> 00:54:32,160
That's why I told you
not to get your hopes up.

1012
00:54:34,400 --> 00:54:36,400
I really didn't see this coming.

1013
00:54:37,460 --> 00:54:38,460
Let me ask you something.

1014
00:54:38,960 --> 00:54:40,640
In the next two years,

1015
00:54:41,320 --> 00:54:44,920
would you treat him the same way you did
at the BBQ place?

1016
00:54:46,200 --> 00:54:47,680
What does that have to do
with what I said?

1017
00:54:48,160 --> 00:54:49,400
Were you listening to me?

1018
00:54:49,720 --> 00:54:50,560
Come on.

1019
00:54:51,280 --> 00:54:52,160
Answer me.

1020
00:55:00,520 --> 00:55:02,280
My love is devoted to him,

1021
00:55:02,840 --> 00:55:04,040
and I'll never give up.

1022
00:55:05,360 --> 00:55:06,640
All I care about is

1023
00:55:06,960 --> 00:55:09,320
whether he likes something
or wants something...

1024
00:55:10,720 --> 00:55:13,040
If he wants me to
grill some pork for him, I'll do it.

1025
00:55:14,320 --> 00:55:16,040
If he wants me to
peel grilled shrimp for him, I'll do it.

1026
00:55:20,040 --> 00:55:21,400
If he no longer wants it,

1027
00:55:24,600 --> 00:55:25,600
I'll stop.

1028
00:55:26,600 --> 00:55:27,720
That's how I see it.

1029
00:55:30,360 --> 00:55:31,080
Mm.

1030
00:55:34,240 --> 00:55:35,440
Warrior, I hate you.

1031
00:55:36,800 --> 00:55:38,000
You're trying to be so emotional.

1032
00:55:39,800 --> 00:55:40,800
That's it.

1033
00:55:41,120 --> 00:55:42,120
Keep it going.

1034
00:55:42,960 --> 00:55:44,360
If something bothers you,

1035
00:55:44,400 --> 00:55:45,800
just vent to me.

1036
00:55:53,480 --> 00:55:54,480
Shit.

1037
00:55:54,800 --> 00:55:55,880
Something big is coming up.

1038
00:55:56,560 --> 00:55:57,280
What?

1039
00:55:57,840 --> 00:55:58,880
Seven-one-five-three.

1040
00:55:58,920 --> 00:56:00,200
Seven-one-five-three.

1041
00:56:00,700 --> 00:56:03,280
Seven-one-five-three.

1042
